posts.content: There I was 7.45am Friday morning sat at the computer eagerly awaiting Car Fest tickets ,bet there was a few of you too? 8.00 am tickets on sale . By 8.02 yep 2 minutes all the family tickets and campervan tickets SOLD! .... A Year of anticipation,excitement gone in 2 minutes...........NEED I SAY MORE !
Hang on in there, more are going on sale

Well I forgot to mention,i was so pi**ed off with yet again missing out on tickets,today I went into the garage and started to dismantle the bus for a full resto and I've given up on any shows for "HERMAN" next year would of been his and mine first season ! More frustration !! can't manage to upload pictures either. In fact I could take over and ***** about allsorts at mo!

Well if this is a things that have ...... you off thread then....... My computer runs windows vista which is the aids of the computer world. It took me 4 hours to load 4 pics to the 'view from the split' thread and load 14 songs!!!! The computer froze half a dozen times
Had to add this to my earlier moan,to even things out applied for Glastonbury tickets yesterday and WHOOPEE !!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!! GOT EM'.
